## Stack

- **Python 3.12+** -- modern type hints, pattern matching
- **Click** -- composable CLI with built-in help
- **Requests** -- battle-tested HTTP client
- **pytest + pytest-cov** -- test runner with coverage
- **Ruff** -- fast Python linter (E, F, I, N, W, UP, B, SIM)
- **mypy (strict)** -- static type checking
- **Hatchling** -- modern PEP 517 build backend

